<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA80">
<l>piṟappiṟappu mūppup piṇituṟantu piṉṉu</l>
<l>miṟakkavu miṉpuṭaittā mēlum maṟappellā</l>
<l>mētamē yeṉṟallā leṇṇuvaṉē maṇṇaḷantāṉ</l>
<l>pātamē yēttāp pakal.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Even if we were to have the pleasure to abandon other births,</l>
<l>old age [and] sickness [and] moreover to go beyond, in all oblivion,</l>
<l>would I count a day of not praising the feet of him who measured</l>
<l>the world other than affliction?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
